icate hand to touch his arm gently, and Mylo felt a warm, tingling sensation spread throughout his body. He knew that he had found someone special in Amara.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" data-src=\"https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/DALL\u00b7E-2023-04-24-14.18.26-Oil-painting-of-a-happy-rosy-cheeked-amanita-muscaria-mushroom-clasping-his-hands-together-scrunching-her-face-in-joy-1024x604.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5736 lazyload\"\/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"604\" src=\"https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/DALL\u00b7E-2023-04-24-14.18.26-Oil-painting-of-a-happy-rosy-cheeked-amanita-muscaria-mushroom-clasping-his-hands-together-scrunching-her-face-in-joy-1024x604.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5736 lazyload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/DALL\u00b7E-2023-04-24-14.18.26-Oil-painting-of-a-happy-rosy-cheeked-amanita-muscaria-mushroom-clasping-his-hands-together-scrunching-her-face-in-joy-1024x604.png 1024w, https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/DALL\u00b7E-2023-04-24-14.18.26-Oil-painting-of-a-happy-rosy-cheeked-amanita-muscaria-mushroom-clasping-his-hands-together-scrunching-her-face-in-joy-300x177.png 300w, https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/DALL\u00b7E-2023-04-24-14.18.26-Oil-painting-of-a-happy-rosy-cheeked-amanita-muscaria-mushroom-clasping-his-hands-together-scrunching-her-face-in-joy-768x453.png 768w, https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/DALL\u00b7E-2023-04-24-14.18.26-Oil-painting-of-a-happy-rosy-cheeked-amanita-muscaria-mushroom-clasping-his-hands-together-scrunching-her-face-in-joy-1536x906.png 1536w, https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/DALL\u00b7E-2023-04-24-14.18.26-Oil-pai